'''Ashley''' is the girlfriend of [[Kyle Rexton]].


Ashley came to the hospital when she learned that her boyfriend, Kyle, was there. He tried to tell her to leave because he did not want her to see him like that, but she stayed anyway. When they learned that Kyle had a condition that was treatable in surgery and that Amelia would do it that day pro bono, they were very happy. Kyle's surgery went well. Afterward, they happily kissed in celebration.\ua



She is dating [[Kyle Rexton]]. She says the war changed him, as before, he was a funny, happy guy.
